description: Wrapper for getopenwater.com REST APIs. Full featured read/write API for the most popular application and review platform.
releaseNotes:
PLEASE READ CAREFULLY BEFORE UPDATING PACKAGE. THIS VERSION CONTAINS BREAKING CHANGES.

Changelog:
 + Renamed `SchedulerEventTargetType` enum to `SchedulerItemTargetType`
 + Added inline scores support for table field rows
 + Added scheduler endpoints support

* Breaking changes (order of arguments has changed):
  - [Fields]:
    + ApplicationNameFieldModel: `firstTitle`, `secondTitle` arguments become optional
    + FileUploadFieldModel: `allowedFileExtensions`, `captionLabel` arguments become optional
    + LetterOfRecommendationFieldModel: `confirmationPageHtml` argument becomes optional
    + MultilineTextFieldModel: `allowedHtmlTags` argument becomes optional
    + NumberFieldModel: `format` argument becomes optional
    + TableFieldModel: `rowName`, `rowNamePlural` and `rowTemplate` arguments become optional.
 
  - [Request models]:
    + ChangeFinalizedRoundSubmissionStatusRequest: `status` argument becomes required.

  - [Field values]:
    + LetterOfRecommendationFieldValueModel: `email`, `fullName` arguments become optional.

* Not breaking changes:
 - [Field values]:
    + AddressFieldValueModel: `city`, `countryCode`, `line2`, `line3`, `state`, `street` and `zip` arguments become optional
    + ApplicationNameFieldValueModel: `firstValue`, `secondValue` arguments become optional
    + DigitalSignatureFieldValueModel: `value` argmuent becomes optional
    + FileUploadFieldValueModel: `caption` argument becomes optional
    + ImisNumberFieldValueModel: `result`, `value` arguments become optional
    + SessionNameFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional
    + TextFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional
    + WysiwygFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional.

 - [Misc]
    + Fixed DateTimeOffset handling on HTTP GET requests, when DateTime formatted in UTC instead of local without timezone.
